  body
    // Navigation 2.0
    nav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-dark.bg-dark.fixed-top
      .container
        button.btn.btn-dark.d-inline-block.d-lg-none.ml-auto(type='button', data-toggle='collapse', data-target='#navbarSupportedContent', aria-controls='navbarSupportedContent', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
          i.fas.fa-align-justify
        #navbarSupportedContent.collapse.navbar-collapse
          h6.lyric DateU
          ul.nav.navbar-nav.ml-auto
            li.nav-item.active
              a.nav-link(href='#') Home
            li.nav-item
              a.nav-link(href='#') About
            li.nav-item
              a.register.nav-link.btn-primary(href='/users/login') Login/Register
    header
      #myCarousel.profile-container
        ul.carousel-indicators
          li.item1.active
          li.item2
          li.item3
        .carousel-inner
          .carousel-item.active.item.b1
            .header-content.text-center
              h1.h1-responsive.text-center.he2.lyric2
                | Make your confession and  
                br
                | start to meet new people!
          .carousel-item.item.b2
            .header-content.text-center
              h1.h1-responsive.text-center.he4.lyric2
                | Find your partner and 
                br
                | enjoy new experiences
              a.btn.btn-primary(href='/users/login') Registrar
          .carousel-item.item.b3
            .header-content.text-center
              h1.h1-responsive.float-md-left.he3.lyric2
                | Meet a lot of UCA's students
                br
                | with common tastes.
        a.carousel-control-prev(href='#myCarousel')
          span.carousel-control-prev-icon
        a.carousel-control-next(href='#myCarousel')
          span.carousel-control-next-icon
    // Page Content
    section.sec1.my-bg2
      .container
        .heading1.text-center
          h3.subhead A new trend
          h1.display-1.display-1--light.mb-5 Welcome to Date U
        p.p1
          | Date U comes from the idea of ​​5 students of the UCA, we think that there should be an easier way to get to know other 
          | students that are not from our career or are from different years and that in a personal way it is difficult to do so. 
          | DateU consists in making confessions to other students of the university, and if the other person likes it, we have 
          | achieved our goal. Not only can you meet people to have an appointment with them, you can also do with other reasons
          | such as just looking for a friendship or talking about university terms, to study. With this project we try to improve 
          | a little the social life of the university students knowing other students that possibly have the same tastes as the other.
    section.gray-bg.section-padding
      .container
        .row
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-4
            .box.box1
              .box-icon
              i.fas.fa-user-friends.mb-5
              h4 Find Friends
              p
              | Find new people with whom you can forge new friendships and experiences.
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-4
            .box
              .box-icon
              i.fas.fa-heart.mb-5
              h4 Find Love
              p
              | Send your confession to the girl / boy that attracts you and let luck decide what can happen.
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-4
            .box.box3
              .box-icon
                i.fas.fa-book.mb-5
                h4 Find other students!
                p
              | You can meet to study with other students who may have already taken your subject and need help.
  
    section.gray-bg.section-padding.my-bg
      .container
        .row
          .col-xs-12.col-sm-12
            .box.box2
              .box-icon
              i.fas.fa-comments.mb-5.myw
              h4.myw Use the Global Chat
              p.myw
              | If you want, you can use the global chat, with these you can chat with anybody that is in this chat too,
              | all you gotta do is to give yourself a nickname, then you can start to chat!.
          
    .contac
      section.container.mb-4
        h1.display-1.text-center.my-4 Contact us
        p.text-center.w-responsive.mx-auto.mb-5
          | Let us know how you feel!
        .row
          .col-md-9.mb-md-0.mb-5
            form#contact-form(name='contact-form', action='mail.php', method='POST')
              .row
                .col-md-6
                  .md-form.mb-0
                    input#name.form-control(type='text', name='name')
                    label(for='name') Your name
                .col-md-6
                  .md-form.mb-0
                    input#email.form-control(type='text', name='email')
                    label(for='email') UCA's email
              .row
                .col-md-12
                  .md-form.mb-0
                    input#subject.form-control(type='text', name='subject')
                    label(for='subject') Subject
              .row
                .col-md-12
                  .md-form
                    textarea#message.form-control.md-textarea(type='text', name='message', rows='2')
                    label(for='message') Your Message
            .text-center.text-md-left
               a.btn.btn-primary(onclick="document.getElementById('contact-form').submit();") Send
            .status
          .col-md-3.text-center
             ul.list-unstyled.mb-0
               li
                 i.fa.fa-map-marker.fa-2x
                 p Bulevar Los Proceres, El Salvador
               li
                 i.fa.fa-phone.mt-4.fa-2x
                 p +503 2257-7777
               li
                 i.fa.fa-envelope.mt-4.fa-2x
                 p contact@dateu.club
        

              


